Off to a party everyone, c ya all tomorrow.

::Reptilica/Ramulus::

Reptilica nods. "Allright, whatever suits ya."

He looks back to make sure no one was following. He frowns. Why would 
anyone follow anyways? "We're about halfway there. Don't know why 
Phobia wanted to fight into a Pred base for CR chambers."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
As Fliq's body expands, Ramulus' mind becomes fully conscious. With 
curiosity, his spark finds some info on the body he was in. It wasn't 
quite like Fliq's, but it was a bit familliar to his...

(I'm fine), he replies as he hears Fliq's voice from nowhere, (Did 
the repair work?)
